        public Module(java.lang.String id,
      java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.String> clashedModules,
      java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,java.lang.Integer> coupledModules,
      int examLength,
      int moduleSize,
      java.lang.String type)
        Constructor for objects of type module
        Parameters:
        id - - id of the module
        clashedModules- - arraylist of modules that need to be clashed with this module(ran at the same time as the module)
        coupledModules- - arraylist of modules that need to be couple with this module(cannot be ran at the same time as the module because the students do both these modules so they cannot be at the same place at the same time)
        examLength- - the length of the exam for this module
        moduleSize- - the number of people who do this module
        type- - the type of room which the exam needs to be conducted in
